org.stekikun.dolmen.unparam

Class Production.Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.stekikun.dolmen.unparam.Production.Item
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Production.ActionItem, Production.Actual, Production.Continue
    Enclosing class:
    Production

    public abstract static class Production.Item
extends Object
    The base class for production items. Items can either be actuals when they reference a terminal or non-terminal of the grammar, or semantic actions which are propagated in the generated parser code.

    An extra special kind of item is the continuation which allows to reenter the current rule and can only be used last in a production.
